            "id": "4553743",
            "title": "Airbus SE GAAP EPS of Є3.27 beats by Є0.50, revenue of Є25.98B misses by Є790M; gives FY26 outlook",
            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li>Airbus SE <a href=\"https://www.airbus.com/sites/g/files/jlcbta136/files/2026-02/press-release-airbus-fy2025-results_hm0612.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">press release</a>  (EADSF): Q4  GAAP EPS of Є3.27  beats by Є0.50.</li>\n<li>Revenue of Є25.98B (+5.1% Y/Y)  misses by Є790M.</li>\n<li>Q4 2025 EBIT Adjusted increased by 17%.</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Outlook:</strong>  The Company’s 2026 guidance is before M&amp;A and includes the impact of currently applicable tariffs. On that basis, the Company targets to achieve in 2026:</li>\n<li>Around 870 commercial aircraft deliveries;</li>\n<li>EBIT Adjusted of around € 7.5 billion;</li>\n<li>Free Cash Flow before Customer Financing of around € 4.5 billion.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
