            "title": "Quant ratings on Coatue Management's top holdings: TSM, MSFT, META, AMZN",
            "description": "<html><body><p data-eci=\"true\">Coatue Management, the technology-focused investment firm led by founder and portfolio manager Philippe Laffont, made notable shifts in both position size and allocation between Q4 2024 and Q4 2025. The fund remains heavily concentrated in the information technology, consumer discretionary, and communication sectors.</p>\n<p>Coatue considerably expanded its position in Netflix (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NFLX\" title=\"Netflix, Inc.\">NFLX</a>) from ~618,735 shares in Q4 2025 to over 10.86M shares in Q4 2025. Lam Research (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/LRCX\" title=\"Lam Research Corporation\">LRCX</a>) allocation grew 142% Y/Y to 9.81M shares. The fund also added Alphabet (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GOOG\" title=\"Alphabet Inc.\">GOOG</a>), increasing its position by 396% Y/Y to 2M shares. Other companies where the fund strengthened its position include Microsoft (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MSFT\" title=\"Microsoft Corporation\">MSFT</a></span></span></span>), Spotify (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SPOT\" title=\"Spotify Technology S.A.\">SPOT</a>), DoorDash (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DASH\" title=\"DoorDash, Inc.\">DASH</a>), and Broadcom (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AVGO\" title=\"Broadcom Inc.\">AVGO</a>).</p>\n<p>Among the companies that were newly added to the portfolio in 2025 are Oracle (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ORCL\" title=\"Oracle Corporation\">ORCL</a>), Synopsys (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SNPS\" title=\"Synopsys, Inc.\">SNPS</a>), Snowflake (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SNOW\" title=\"Snowflake Inc.\">SNOW</a>), ARM Holdings (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ARM\" title=\"Arm Holdings plc\">ARM</a>), Rocket Companies (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/RKT\" title=\"Rocket Companies, Inc.\">RKT</a>), and others.</p>\n<p>On the other hand, Coatue trimmed its position in Tesla (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TSLA\" title=\"Tesla, Inc.\">TSLA</a>) by 24% Y/Y to 1.64M shares in Q4 2025. Its Nvidia (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NVDA\" title=\"NVIDIA Corporation\">NVDA</a>) holdings were cut by 8%, from 10M in Q4 2024 to 9.2M in Q4 2025. The fund also cut its holdings in Amazon by 7% Y/Y to 9.93M shares. Among other names where the manager chopped holdings are Adobe (ADBO), Advanced Micro Devices (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AMD\" title=\"Advanced Micro Devices, Inc.\">AMD</a>), Nu Holdings (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NU\" title=\"Nu Holdings Ltd.\">NU</a>), Vertiv Holdings (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/VRT\" title=\"Vertiv Holdings Co\">VRT</a>), and PayPal (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PYPL\" title=\"PayPal Holdings, Inc.\">PYPL</a>).<strong> </strong></p>\n<p>Top names that the fund completely exited in 2025 are Alibaba (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BABA\" title=\"Alibaba Group Holding Limited\">BABA</a>), Zillow Group (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ZG\" title=\"Zillow Group, Inc.\">ZG</a>), HubSpot (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/HUBS\" title=\"HubSpot, Inc.\">HUBS</a>), DataDog (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DDOG\" title=\"Datadog, Inc.\">DDOG</a>), Dell Technologies (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DELL\" title=\"Dell Technologies Inc.\">DELL</a>), Eli Lilly (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/LLY\" title=\"Eli Lilly and Company\">LLY</a>), among others.</p>\n<p><strong>Check SA quant ratings on Coatue Management's top 15 holdings:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Taiwan Semiconductor Manufacturing Company (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TSM\" title=\"Taiwan Semiconductor Manufacturing Company Limited\">TSM</a></span></span></span>) – Quant <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TSM/ratings/quant-ratings\">rating</a>: 3.49 out of 5 – Hold</li>\n<li>Microsoft (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MSFT\" title=\"Microsoft Corporation\">MSFT</a>) – Quant <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MSFT/ratings/quant-ratings\">rating</a>: 3.49 out of 5 – Hold</li>\n<li>Meta Platforms (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/META\" title=\"Meta Platforms, Inc.\">META</a></span></span></span>) – Quant <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/META/ratings/quant-ratings\">rating</a> : 3.39 out of 5 – Hold</li>\n<li>Amazon (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AMZN\" title=\"Amazon.com, Inc.\">AMZN</a></span></span></span>) – Quant <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AMZN/ratings/quant-ratings\">rating</a>: 3.41 out of 5 – Hold</li>\n<li>GE Vernova (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GEV\" title=\"GE Vernova Inc.\">GEV</a>) – Quant <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GEV/ratings/quant-ratings\">rating</a>: 3.46 out of 5 – Hold</li>\n<li>Alphabet (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GOOGL\" title=\"Alphabet Inc.\">GOOGL</a>) – Quant <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GOOGL/ratings/quant-ratings\">rating</a>: 3.48 out of 5 – Hold</li>\n<li>Constellation Energy (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CEG\" title=\"Constellation Energy Corporation\">CEG</a>) – <span> </span>Quant <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CEG/ratings/quant-ratingshttps:/seekingalpha.com/symbol/CEG/ratings/quant-ratings\">rating</a>: 2.17 out of 5 – Sell</li>\n<li>Broadcom (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AVGO\" title=\"Broadcom Inc.\">AVGO</a>) – Quant <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AVGO/ratings/quant-ratings\">rating</a>: 3.49 out of 5 – Hold</li>\n<li>Nvidia (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NVDA\" title=\"NVIDIA Corporation\">NVDA</a>) – Quant <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NVDA/ratings/quant-ratings\">rating</a>: 3.49 out of 5 – Hold</li>\n<li>Lam Research (LRXC) – Quant <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/LRCX/ratings/quant-ratings\">rating</a>: 3.49 out of 5 – Hold</li>\n<li>Applied Materials (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AMAT\" title=\"Applied Materials, Inc.\">AMAT</a>) – Quant <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AMAT/ratings/quant-ratings\">rating</a>: 3.49 out of 5 – Hold</li>\n<li>Eaton Corporation (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ETN\" title=\"Eaton Corporation plc\">ETN</a>) – Quant <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ETN/ratings/quant-ratings\">rating</a>: 2.83 out of 5 – Hold</li>\n<li>AppLovin (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/APP\" title=\"AppLovin Corporation\">APP</a>) – Quant <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/APP/ratings/quant-ratings\">rating</a>: 3.25 out of 5 – Hold</li>\n<li>Spotify Technology (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SPOT\" title=\"Spotify Technology S.A.\">SPOT</a>) – Quant <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SPOT/ratings/quant-ratings\">rating</a>: 3.21 out of 5 – Hold</li>\n<li>Reddit (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/RDDT\" title=\"Reddit, Inc.\">RDDT</a>) – Quant <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/RDDT/ratings/quant-ratings\">rating</a>: 3.14 out of 5 – Hold</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
